Hi all,

A small clarification on the NAMESPACE stuff...

Q: If I use a NAMESPACE and have S4 classes or methods in my package,
   do I need to define a .onLoad function that require()'s methods.

A: Yes.

   See the Writing R Extensions manual for how to.  See this post for
   some explanation:
   https://stat.ethz.ch/pipermail/r-devel/2005-November/035585.html


